object.customQuery:
select * from (select isnull(sd.OpenedDt,'9999-12-31') as LossAccountEnteredDate,substring(rk.riskstate,1,2) as riskstate,cd.claimnumber,cd.CatGroupDesc,cd.LosscauseCd,
cd.subLosscauseCd,l.GW_LOB_Desc as LineOfBusiness,l.GW_LOB_Group_Desc as LOB_group,
isnull(sd.OpenedDt,'9999-12-31') as OpenedDt,isnull(sd.ClosedDt,'9999-12-31') as ClosedDt,
isnull(cd.LossReportedDt,'9999-12-31') as ReportedDt,
case when sd.TotalRecoveryAmt>0 then abs(datediff(day,sd.ClosedDt,sd.openeddt)) else 0 end as Cycle_Time_Files_With_Recovery,
case when sd.TotalRecoveryAmt<=0 then abs(datediff(day,sd.ClosedDt,sd.openeddt)) else 0 end as Cycle_Time_Files_Without_Recovery,
ltrim(rtrim(sd.SubrogationStatusCd)) as SubrogationStatusCd,
case when sd.TotalRecoveryAmt>0 then 'Recovered' else 'Not Recovered' end as Subro_success_Status,
0 as LossPaidAmt,sd.Demand as Demand,
ct.SubroExpenseAmt as Subro_Expense_Amt,ct.SubroExpenseAmt as Allocated_Loss_Adjustment_Expense,
isnull(sd.TotalRecoveryAmt,0) as TotalRecoveryAmt,sd.DeductibleReturnedAmt as Deductible_returned,cd.ClaimType,'OpenedDt-Dashboard' as Dashboard_Indicator
,sd.SubrogationExaminer
,sd.SubrogationLegalCounsel
from dbo.subrogationdetail sd (nolock)
left join (select * from dbo.Claimdetail where RowEffEndDt = '9999-12-31 00:00:00.0000000') cd on cd.policykey=sd.policykey and cd.claimnumber=sd.claimnumber
left join (select claimnumber,policykey,sum(LossPaidAmt) as SubroExpenseAmt from dbo.claimtransaction where classificationcd in ('Subrogation-Legal','Subrogation-Expert','Subrogation-Other') group by claimnumber,policykey)ct
on sd.claimnumber=ct.claimnumber and sd.policykey=ct.policykey
left join dbo.policydetail pd(nolock)  on pd.policykey=sd.policykey
left join (select distinct PolicyKey,RiskState from dbo.Risk where RowEffEndDt = '9999-12-31 00:00:00.0000000')  rk on rk.policykey=sd.policykey
left join dbo.LOB_Ref l on pd.LineOfBusiness = l.GW_LOB_Desc
where sd.claimnumber like '%CLM%'

union all

select isnull(ct.LossAccountEnteredDate,'9999-12-31') as LossAccountEnteredDate,'NA' as riskstate,ct.claimnumber,cd.CatGroupDesc,'NA' as LosscauseCd,
'NA' as subLosscauseCd
,l.GW_LOB_Desc as LineOfBusiness,l.GW_LOB_Group_Desc as LOB_group
,'8888-01-01' as OpenedDt,'8888-01-01' as ClosedDt
,cd.LossReportedDt as ReportedDt,
0 as Cycle_Time_Files_With_Recovery,
0 as Cycle_Time_Files_Without_Recovery,
'NA' as SubrogationStatusCd,
'NA' as Subro_success_Status,
sum(ct.LossPaidAmt),0 as Demand,
0 as Subro_Expense_Amt,0 as Allocated_Loss_Adjustment_Expense,
0 as TotalRecoveryAmt,0 as Deductible_returned,'NA' as ClaimType,'OpenedDt-Dashboard' as Dashboard_Indicator
,NULL as SubrogrationExaminer
,NULL as SubrogationLegalCounsel
from dbo.claimtransaction ct
left join (select * from dbo.Claimdetail where RowEffEndDt = '9999-12-31 00:00:00.0000000') cd on cd.claimnumber=ct.claimnumber
left join dbo.PolicyDetail pd (nolock) on ct.PolicyKey = pd.PolicyKey
left join dbo.LOB_Ref L (nolock) on pd.LineOfBusiness = l.GW_LOB_Desc
where ct.claimnumber like '%CLM%' and cd.CatGroupDesc='Non-Cat' group by ct.LossAccountEnteredDate,ct.claimnumber,cd.CatGroupDesc
,l.GW_LOB_Desc,l.GW_LOB_Group_Desc,cd.LossReportedDt) where claimnumber='CLM-00016768' and losscausecd!='NA'
